text: Zhang Mingyu (born 3 October 2001) is a female Chinese modern pentathlete. In 2018 she won the gold medal in the women's individual event at the 2018 Asian Games held in Jakarta, Indonesia. == References == == External links == * * Category:Living people Category:2001 births Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Chinese female modern pentathletes Category:Asian Games medalists in modern pentathlon Category:Modern pentathletes at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games gold medalists for China Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games
